import React, { Component } from "react";
import {
  Col,
  Row,
  Button,
  Form,
  FormGroup,
  Label,
  Input,
  Container
} from "reactstrap";

export default class FormComponent extends Component {
  state = {
  }

  render() {
    return (
      <Container>
        <Form>
          <Row>
            <Col sm={6} lg={6} xl={6}>
              <FormGroup>
                <Label for="exampleEmail" sm={2}>
                  Nama
                </Label>
                <Col sm={10}>
                  <Input
                    type="text"
                    name="nama"
                    placeholder="Nama Penuh"
                  />
                </Col>
              </FormGroup>
            </Col>
            <Col sm={6} lg={6} xl={6}>
              <FormGroup>
                <Label for="exampleEmail" sm={2}>
                  Alamat
                </Label>
                <Col sm={10}>
                  <Input
                    type="text"
                    name="alamat"
                    placeholder="Full name"
                  />
                </Col>
              </FormGroup>
            </Col>
            <Col sm={6} lg={6} xl={6}>
              <FormGroup>
                <Label check>
                  <Input type="checkbox" id="checkbox2" value="1" />{' '}
                  Status
                </Label>
              </FormGroup>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Form>
      </Container>
    );
  }
}
